definitions.definition: A special ward of Tokyo prefecture , Japan that is surrounded by (clockwise from north) Saitama Prefecture, Nerima , Nakano , Shibuya , Setagaya special wards, and two cities in Western Tokyo ( Mitaka and Musashino ).
